org.openhubframework.openhub.core.common.asynch

Class TraceHeaderProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openhubframework.openhub.core.common.asynch.TraceHeaderProcessor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.camel.Processor

    public class TraceHeaderProcessor
extends Object
implements org.apache.camel.Processor
    Processor that gain trace header information and save it as message header TRACE_HEADER in exchange.

    Processor works with our input asynchronous messages (trace header is in SOAP header) and also with input messages (trace header is in SOAP body).

    Trace header is mandatory by default but you can change it.

    Author:
    Petr Juza
